&lt;p&gt;运行所给的程序 socket 通信相关&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img data-src=&#34;/images/image-20230909162510993.png&#34; alt=&#34;image-20230909162510993&#34;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
